  "text": "In order to prove the cartilage complete layer injury, the cartilage tissue samples which were taken from each of 6 rats from both groups were also evaluated histopathologically. The samples were buried in paraffin-embedded blocks after the routine tissue monitoring. Five-micron sections were put to hematoxylineosin staining and examined in the light microscope (×100). Histological sections were examined in terms of 8 parameters and scored and evaluated [CITATION_1] .",
